        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 55. Cnemaspis kendallii. Left: adult female (LSUDPC 4903) from Santubong, Sarawak, East Malaysia in the light color pattern phase. Upper right: adult male (LSUDPC 4875) from Gunung Gading, Sarawak, East Malaysia in the dark color pattern phase. Photographs by LLG. Lower right: adult male (LSUDPC 6804) from Pulau Karimata, Kalimantan, Indonesia. Photograph by Umilaela Arafin." ;
